text: Saif al-Arab al-Gaddafi (1982 - April 30, 2011) was one of the sons of the former Libyan dictator Muammar al-Gaddafi. His name meant "Sword of the Arabs." He was killed in an air strike by NATO on 31 April 2011. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Libyan people es:Muamar el Gadafi#Familia Gadafi
title: Saif al-Arab Gaddafi
